==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Irresponsibility
<hw>Ir`re*spon`si*bil"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>irresponsabilit⟦eacute⟧</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Lack of, or
freedom from, responsibility or accountability.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A trait causing one to act without a proper sense of
responsibility; acting without giving proper weight to one's
responsibilities.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Irresponsible</ent>⟦br⟧
